config USE_OPENURMA
    bool "Enable OpenURMA UBController SimObject"
    default y
    help
      Adds the UBController SimObject that wraps libopenurma_sc.a inside
      gem5 via the SystemC TLM bridge. Requires the OPENURMA_ROOT
      environment variable and the libopenurma_sc.a static library.
